Artificer Theoric is without question the most capable smith the City of Light has known for generations. He is no man of great theological knowledge and has no skill in holding sermons, but his work with the hammer and anvil has earned him great respect among fellow artisans of the city-state. His works are sought by anyone who understands the trade and tend to fetch unrivaled prices on the market.

Value.value: *he wipes his brow* Time for work. Glad to be back in business. Make sure to stop by and see our merchants' wares!
